 than that i wouldnt say im a tough person tamara mellon man moments step men always look smart in a wellfitted tailored suit conversely they can be incredibly handsome in jeans combined with a cashmere jumper or a beatenup leather jacket or even just a cotton tshirt tamara mellon smart men handsome a little jewellery on a man is ok although he should never wear too much every man should always have a great watch tamara mellon great man too much my worst date would be with someone nervous who has nothing to say i like people who inspire me tamara mellon inspire people me as a business ambassador i am delighted to help both new and established british designers receive the recognition they deserve in the global fashion arena tamara mellon business i am fashion the truth is that we all have lives that are complicated we all get hurt by people we love sometimes its laughable to believe that anyone is immune the important thing is how you behave tamara mellon love truth hurt i dont really understand what the public perception of me is i think public perception and reality are two wholly different things tamara mellon perception reality me people who are overeducated become riskaverse tamara mellon people become who i think it takes  years to build a luxury brand tamara mellon brand think luxury its important for women to work they need to keep their independence to keep earning and being challenged tamara mellon work women independence i actually have more shoes than anyone will ever know tamara mellon shoes know more when someone asks about a career in fashion i say start at the bottom if you want to start a business you have to know it from the ground up tamara mellon business fashion start i always knew i wanted to make my own way i never wanted to be dependent on my father tamara mellon father way my own i just cant see myself as a trophy wife i cant imagine not having my own life tamara mellon life myself wife the thing about uggs is that theyre so comfortable once youve worn them you dont want to go back tamara mellon want you comfortable the reality is that i spent years in the factories in italy when i first set up jimmy choo today everyone who has a job at jimmy choo ive done their job  right down to the cleaner tamara mellon today job reality if i wasnt in fashion i would have been a psychiatrist tamara mellon fashion been psychiatrist when you get divorced you have to go through this awful thing of listing everything you own when you actually sit down and write the list you realize that the only good investments are art and property tamara mellon art good realize my mother and i never got along not even when i was a child tamara mellon mother child never share this page cite this page citation find on amazon tamara mellon related authors coco chanel karl lagerfeld charles eames marc jacobs vera wang william morris alexander mcqueen yves saint laurent brainyquote desktop brainyquote mobile site home authors topics quote of the day pictures top  quotes professions birthdays social bq on facebook bq on twitter bq on pinterest bq on google bq on instagram shop brainyquote store apps iphoneipad app quote of the day feeds javascript and rss feeds wordpress plugin quote of the day email about about us contact us submit privacy terms copyright     brainyquote language espa√±ol  fran√ßais ¬† loading load more quotes womens flats  tamara mellon fit guide the fit is everything i‚Äôve walked in all of my shoes to ensure the perfect fit our size eu uk us jp aus                                                                            questions about fit contact us back to shopping yes please no thank you  the frontline new pumps sandals flats boots bags shop all editions celestial editionnew warrior edition red edition starlight edition neon yellow edition shop all editions our story at your service sign in free shipping  returns free shipping  returns home  collection  flats flats flatline  patent  black flatline  specchio  platin