er engagement to michael ovitz in a magazine interview with hello it has since been revealed that ovitz is still married to his first wife judy she recently referred to the situation as ‚Äúcomplicated‚Äù booksedit mellon tamara william patrick  in my shoes a memoir new york portfoliopenguin isbn¬† oclc¬†¬† referencesedit  a b tamara mellon wwwvoguecouk¬†  a b c d e beeshyuan chang  october  tamara mellons next step the new york times¬†  official website at tamaramelloncom retrieved ¬†  susan berfield  october  jimmy choo cofounder tamara mellon puts on her revenge boots¬†  olivia lidbury  december  tamara mellon has filed for bankruptcy¬†  mulkerrins jane  april  emotional ties with entrepreneur and shoe designer tamara mellon daily mail london¬†  rich list search timesonlinecouk  womens rich list timesonlinecouk  lidbury olivia  december  tamara mellon has filed for bankruptcy the telegraph¬†  milligan laura  december  tamara mellon files for bankruptcy vogue¬†  sunderland ruth  december  how the highliving jimmy choo shoe queen crashed to earth shes david camerons trade ambassador but theres a humiliating new episode in tamara mellons life as her firm goes bankrupt daily mail¬†  evans peter  december  tamara mellon thrown lifeline the sunday times¬†  sabharwal veebs  december  tamara mellon saved from drowning retail gazette¬†  evans peter  january  mellon mauled the sunday times¬†  a b c pavia will  february  don‚Äôt mess with tamara mellon the sunday times¬†  tamara mellon jimmy choo cofounder sues the famed footwear company ‚Äî the fashion law thefashionlawcom  retrieved ¬†    chapman james  november  jimmy choo queen tamara mellon is unveiled as britains new ¬£m trade envoy daily mail london¬†  tamara mellon forbes¬†  revlon website phxcorporateirnet retrieved ¬†  elton john aids foundation patrons ejafcom retrieved ¬†  no  the london gazette supplement  june  p¬†¬†  diamond wendy pioneer awards   winners womens entrepreneurship day retrieved  september ¬†  ta